                    ይህንን የግላዊነት ፖሊሲ በተመለከተ ማንኛቸውም ጥያቄዎች ካሉ ከታች ያለውን መረጃ በመጠቀም ሊያገኙን ይችላሉ።
                </p>
                @if (_PPQM.OperatorType == "Company" || _PPQM.OperatorType == "ኩባንያ")
                {
                    <p>@_PPQM.BusinessName</p>
                }
                else
                {
                    <p>@_PPQM.WebsiteName</p>

                }
                <p> @_PPQM.Address.Subcity ክፍለ ከተማ ወረዳ  @_PPQM.Address.Woreda</p>
                <p>የቤት ቁጥር @_PPQM.Address.HouseNumber</p>

                <p> @_PPQM.Address.Region ፣  @_PPQM.Address.Country</p>
                <p></p>
                @if (_PPQM.Contact.PhoneNumber != null)
                {
                    <p>ስልክ: <a href="tel:@_PPQM.Contact.PhoneNumber">@_PPQM.Contact.PhoneNumber</a></p>
                }
                @if (_PPQM.Contact.Email != null)
